text: Location of Carlisle County in Kentucky This is a list of the National Register of Historic Places listings in Carlisle County, Kentucky. It is intended to be a complete list of the properties on the National Register of Historic Places in Carlisle County, Kentucky, United States. The locations of National Register properties for which the latitude and longitude coordinates are included below, may be seen in a map.
